<div class="card card-body">
  <div class="text-center py-5">
    <h1 class="display-4 mb-4">Let's Get Started!</h1>
    <p class="lead mb-5">
      Where would you want to start?
    </p>
    
    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-4 mb-4">
      <%= link_to "Categories", categories_path, class: "btn btn-outline-grclr btn-lg px-4" %>
      <%= link_to "To-dos", todos_path, class: "btn btn-outline-blclr btn-lg px-4" %>
      <%= link_to "Completed", completed_todos_path, class: "btn btn-outline-grclr btn-lg px-4" %>
    </div>

	<p class=" mb-5">
      Not sure where to start? Start by making a Category. <br> From there you could make more or start making To-dos to place in a category. <br> Always keep track of the status of your To-dos!
    </p>
    

  </div>
</div>